      "datasource": "Prometheus",
      "description": "succeeded / (succeeded + failed). Both counters increment when an attempt COMPLETES, so in-flight lag and rollouts cannot fake a dip (unlike dividing by the send-time requests counter). No data = no completions in the window; a full hang registers once 150s timeouts convert to failures.",
